{
  "info": {
    "name": "Sembremos Seguridad - API",
    "description": "Colección de pruebas manuales para la API del proyecto Sembremos Seguridad.\n\nPrefijos:\n- `/api/v1/auth`\n- `/api/v1/system`\n- `/api/v1/msp/*`\n- `/api/v1/muni/*`\n- `/api/v1/ai/*`\n\nLa autenticación se maneja mediante cookie HTTP-only (`token`). Postman maneja la cookie automáticamente al hacer login. Recordá importar también el environment `sembremos-seguridad.postman_environment.json`.\n\n**Roles posibles:** ADMIN_MSP, OFICIAL_MSP, ADMIN_MUNI, GESTOR_MUNI, SUPER_ADMIN.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_postman_id": "a1b1c1d1-1111-4111-8111-111111111111"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:5000", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "noauth"
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// Asegura que baseUrl exista en el entorno o variable de la colección",
          "if (!pm.variables.get('baseUrl')) {",
          "  pm.variables.set('baseUrl', 'http://localhost:5000');",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "listen": "test",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// Asserts comunes a toda la colección",
          "pm.test('Tiempo de respuesta < 5s', function () {",
          "  pm.expect(pm.response.responseTime).to.be.below(5000);",
          "});",
          "pm.test('Content-Type es JSON cuando hay body', function () {",
          "  if (pm.response.text() && pm.response.text().length > 0) {",
          "    const ct = pm.response.headers.get('Content-Type') || '';",
          "    pm.expect(ct.toLowerCase()).to.include('application/json');",
          "  }",
          "});"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "00 - Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /health",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/health", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["health"] },
            "description": "Verifica que el servidor está arriba. No requiere autenticación."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('status === UP', () => pm.expect(body.status).to.eql('UP'));",
                  "pm.test('timestamp presente', () => pm.expect(body.timestamp).to.be.a('string'));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "01 - Autenticación",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST /system/login (MSP)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{mspEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{mspPassword}}\",\n  \"nivel\": \"MSP\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/system/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "system", "login"] },
            "description": "Login para usuario MSP. La cookie `token` (HTTP-only) queda guardada en Postman al ejecutar."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('status success', () => pm.expect(body.status).to.eql('success'));",
                  "pm.test('Devuelve usuario con id', () => pm.expect(body.data.user).to.have.property('id'));",
                  "pm.test('Nivel === MSP', () => pm.expect(body.data.user.nivel).to.eql('MSP'));",
                  "pm.test('Cookie token recibida', () => {",
                  "  const cookie = pm.cookies.get('token');",
                  "  pm.expect(cookie, 'cookie token').to.exist;",
                  "});",
                  "pm.environment.set('mspUserId', body.data.user.id);",
                  "pm.environment.set('mspUserRol', body.data.user.rol);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /system/login (MUNI)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{muniEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{muniPassword}}\",\n  \"nivel\": \"MUNI\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/system/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "system", "login"] }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Nivel === MUNI', () => pm.expect(body.data.user.nivel).to.eql('MUNI'));",
                  "pm.environment.set('muniUserId', body.data.user.id);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /system/login (credenciales inválidas)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
